STATE
v.
WALKER 2019-0654 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 29, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On motion of Dustin Blake to withdraw as counsel for appellee. Motion granted. Ohio Public Defender's Office appointed to represent appellee and ordered to file an affidavit of indigence executed by appellee within 20 days.
